===Usage notes===
This character is usually written as the bottom component of a character and is not to be confused with {{l|mul|еӨӮ}} which is often written as the top component of a character or {{l|mul|ж”ө}} which is often written as the right component of a character. Traditionally, this character is written with the final [[гҮҸ]] stroke slightly protruding above {{l|mul|гӮҜ}}.

